branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The NCRQ series is a compact rotary, rack and pinion style actuator. The double rack design eliminates backlash and increases strength. Standard equipment include a built-in rubber bumper and rotation adjustment. Auto switch capabilities are an option.
&lt;/p&gt;

